  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_138">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_138</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Ciaran Mullooly</del:name>
    <del:name>Maria Walsh</del:name>
    <del:platform>EU Parliament</del:platform>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_Renew"/>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PPE"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_315">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_315</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Integrate our 27 little armies to fight as one. As President Zelenskyy said, the time has come for the armed forces of Europe to be created. So let's take the first concrete steps today. Make NATO's command and control European so we can operate as one. Jointly procure strategic enablers so we can fight effectively. Create permanent multinational units so we can get 50 extra brigades.
Europe is a peace project, but how can we be strong enough to defend it? The answer to that existential question is simple and consists of three things: Unite! Unite! Unite!
Let's not wait for war to unite us. Let's unite to prevent war. And to my Dutch colleagues in the national parliament who just voted against the REARM plans from Ms von der Leyen, I say you're making a massive mistake.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T17:52:23</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_230"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_314"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_315"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_388">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_388</del:identifier>
    <del:text>On aika aikuistua. PГғВӨГғВӨtГғВ¶kset olisi ollut hyvГғВӨ tehdГғВӨ jo kolme vuotta sitten, mutta satsaamalla puolustukseen nyt voimme kolmen vuoden pГғВӨГғВӨstГғВӨ ehkГғВӨ huokaista helpotuksesta. Ukrainan vahvuus ja tuen jatkuminen on nГғВӨhtГғВӨvГғВӨ Euroopan puolustuksen samanaikaisena synnyttГғВӨmisenГғВӨ.
Liiallinen Amerikka-riippuvuuden karsiminen vaatii eurooppalaisten vaihtoehtojen kehittГғВӨmistГғВӨ. Tilanne, jossa noin 70 prosenttia kaikesta hankinnasta tehdГғВӨГғВӨn Yhdysvalloista, ei ole kestГғВӨvГғВӨ malli. Paljon kestГғВӨvГғВӨmpГғВӨГғВӨ on Euroopan teollisen kapasiteetin valjastaminen painavan pelotteen synnyttГғВӨmiseen.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T19:30:17</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_276"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_387"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_388"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_295">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_295</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Victor Negrescu</del:name>
    <del:platform>EU Parliament</del:platform>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_S&amp;D"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_469">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_469</del:identifier>
    <del:text>En segundo lugar, decisiГғВіn. Necesitamos medidas mГғВЎs concretas y efectivas, porque el plan de energГғВӯa asequible ya se queda corto para la industria electrointensiva, y muchas propuestas como reducir peajes, cargos e impuestos o invertir en redes son solo recomendaciones para los Estados miembros. Y en el caso de EspaГғВұa, empeГғВұada en cerrar las nucleares, me temo que no las seguirГғВЎn.
En tercer lugar, reglas del juego justas. Urge actualizar todos los mecanismos de defensa comercial para que sean efectivos. Lo conoce usted muy bien porque sectores como el acero estГғВЎn en una situaciГғВіn insostenible.
SeГғВұor comisario, podemos hacerlo. Europa ha demostrado histГғВіricamente su capacidad para adaptarse y liderar en tiempos de cambio. Pero debemos actuar ya.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T21:12:22</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_336"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_468"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_469"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_235">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_235</del:identifier>
    <del:text>TakГ…Вҫe pojГ„ВҸme se zamyslet nad tГғВӯm, co jsme udГ„Вӣlali. PojГ„ВҸme Г…ВЎkrtat, pojГ„ВҸme mazat naГ…ВЎi legislativu, pojГ„ВҸme vytvГғВЎГ…Вҷet podmГғВӯnky. A poslednГғВӯ vГ„Вӣc, vy jste tady vГ…ВЎichni mluvili o tom, Г…Вҫe potГ…Вҷebujete penГғВӯze. My tady rozhazujeme kaГ…ВҫdГғВ© plenГғВЎrnГғВӯ zasedГғВЎnГғВӯ stovky miliard. Dejme je koneГ„ВҚnГ„Вӣ na nГ„Вӣco uГ…ВҫiteГ„ВҚnГғВ©ho! A toto je uГ…ВҫiteГ„ВҚnГғВЎ vГ„Вӣc. Toto jsou lГғВ©ky Г…Вҫivot zachraГ…ВҲujГғВӯcГғВӯ a ne zbranГ„Вӣ, kterГғВ© zabГғВӯjejГғВӯ.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:40:46</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_173"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_234"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_235"/>
  </rdf:Description>
