  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_223">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_223</del:identifier>
    <del:text>A betegek helyzetГғВ©nek javГғВӯtГғВЎsa ГғВ©rdekГғВ©ben kiemelten fontos a gyГғВіgyszerek elГғВ©rhetГ…В‘sГғВ©ge ГғВ©s megfizethetГ…В‘sГғВ©ge, mikГғВ¶zben biztosГғВӯtjuk az eurГғВіpai gyГғВіgyszeripar versenykГғВ©pessГғВ©gГғВ©t ГғВ©s rezilienciГғВЎjГғВЎt. Fontos hangsГғВәlyozni, hogy a Critical Medicines Act ne nГғВ¶velje az adminisztratГғВӯv terheket, ГғВ©s ne legyen jogi ГғВЎtfedГғВ©s, pГғВ©ldГғВЎul a gyГғВіgyszercsomaghiГғВЎnnyal foglalkozГғВі rГғВ©szГғВ©vel. ГғВңdvГғВ¶zlГғВ¶m a bemutatott javaslatot, ГғВ©s kГғВ¶szГғВ¶nГғВ¶m VГғВЎrhelyi biztos ГғВәrnak ГғВ©s csapatГғВЎnak, hogy ilyen gyorsan elkГғВ©szГғВӯtettГғВ©k azt.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:25:00</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_166"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_222"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_223"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_540">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_540</del:identifier>
    <del:text>ГҺВҹГҺВ№ ГҺВ»ГҺВұГҺВҝГҺВҜ ГҺВұГҸВҖГҺВұГҺВ№ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВҚГҺВҪ ГҺВҪГҺВұ ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВұГҺВјГҺВұГҸВ„ГҺВ®ГҸВғГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВҪ ГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҺВөГҺВіГҺВәГҺВ»ГҺВ®ГҺВјГҺВұГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВ… ГҸВғГҸВ…ГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҺВұГҺВәГҺВҝГҸВҚ ГҺВәГҺВұГҺВёГҺВөГҸВғГҸВ„ГҸВҺГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВӮ ГҸВҖГҺВҝГҸВ… ГҺВөГҸВҖГҺВ№ГҺВІГҺВ»ГҺВ®ГҺВёГҺВ·ГҺВәГҺВө ГҺВјГҺВө ГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҺВҪ ГҺВ№ГҺВјГҸВҖГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҺВұГҺВ»ГҺВ№ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВ№ГҺВәГҺВ® ГҺВөГҸВҖГҺВӯГҺВјГҺВІГҺВұГҸВғГҺВ· ГҺВ—ГҺВҪГҸВүГҺВјГҺВӯГҺВҪГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҺВ ГҺВҝГҺВ»ГҺВ№ГҸВ„ГҺВөГҺВ№ГҸВҺГҺВҪ, ГҺВҷГҸВғГҸВҒГҺВұГҺВ®ГҺВ» ГҺВәГҺВұГҺВ№ ГҺВӨГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҸВҒГҺВәГҺВҜГҺВұГҸВӮ. ГҺВЈГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҸВҒГҺВҜГҺВ¶ГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВҪ ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҺВҪ ГҺВҙГҺВҜГҺВәГҺВұГҺВ№ГҺВҝ ГҺВұГҺВіГҸВҺГҺВҪГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҺВ ГҺВұГҺВ»ГҺВұГҺВ№ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВ№ГҺВҪГҺВҜГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҺВіГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҺВөГҺВ»ГҺВөГҸВҚГҺВёГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВ·, ГҺВұГҺВҪГҺВөГҺВҫГҺВ¬ГҸВҒГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҸВ„ГҺВ· ГҸВҖГҺВұГҸВ„ГҸВҒГҺВҜГҺВҙГҺВұ ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВҝ ГҸВҖГҺВ»ГҺВ¬ГҺВ№ ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВ… ГҺВҷГҸВғГҸВҒГҺВұГҺВ®ГҺВ», ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҸВғГҸВҚГҺВҪГҺВҝГҸВҒГҺВұ ГҸВҖГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҺВҪ ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҺВҪ ГҺВҷГҺВҝГҸВҚГҺВҪГҺВ· ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВ… ГўВҖВҷ67 ГҺВјГҺВө ГҸВҖГҸВҒГҸВүГҸВ„ГҺВөГҸВҚГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҸВғГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҺВҪ ГҺВұГҺВҪГҺВұГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҺВ»ГҺВ№ГҺВәГҺВ® ГҺВҷГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҸВғГҺВұГҺВ»ГҺВ®ГҺВј, ГҺВөГҺВҪГҺВ¬ГҺВҪГҸВ„ГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҺВөГҸВҖГҺВ№ГҺВәГҺВҜГҺВҪГҺВҙГҸВ…ГҺВҪГҺВұ ГҸВғГҸВҮГҺВӯГҺВҙГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҺВ—ГҺВ ГҺВ‘-ГҺВҷГҸВғГҸВҒГҺВұГҺВ®ГҺВ» ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҺВҪ ГҸВҖГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҺВҝГҸВҮГҺВ®.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T23:01:32</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_24"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_539"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_540"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_355">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_355</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Qui dit sГғВ©curitГғВ© des peuples dit aussi sГғВ©curitГғВ© sociale. DГғВ©fense et sГғВ©curitГғВ© sociale vont de pair ГўВҖВ“ГӮВ lutte contre la pauvretГғВ©, logement, santГғВ©, retraites, et jГўВҖВҷen passeГўВҖВҰ
Enfin, Monsieur le Commissaire, pensez-vous vraiment qu'il soit possible de construire une Europe de la dГғВ©fense avec 27ГӮВ pays? Vu l'urgence, ne faudrait-il pas inciter un groupe restreint dГўВҖВҷГғВүtats membres ГғВ  aller de lГўВҖВҷavant ГғВ  ce sujet, comme nous lГўВҖВҷavions fait pour Schengen?</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T18:49:42</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_256"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_354"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_355"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_23">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_23</del:identifier>
    <del:text>I see a hand up there. Go ahead, MrГӮВ Panayiotou. Sorry, MrГӮВ Sieper. I can't see that far.</del:text>
    <del:text></del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T17:21:56</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T10:12:13</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_20"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_22"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_23"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_169">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_169</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Many of the citizens that voted for their countries to enter the Union after the 1990s did so with the hope that their countries and societies will converge to these European values.
What we are seeing in the Commission work programme is that the anti-discrimination directive ГўВҖВ“ and many other measures for which we did not reach an agreement in five years ГўВҖВ“ gets withdrawn.
This means that the Council gets handed the perfect weapon: if they ever think that we're asking for too much in the Parliament or in the Commission, they just need to drag their feet for long enough and then make the problem disappear.
In the meantime, the message we are sending to Europeans is clear: these values you hoped for will remain unreachable.
It is unacceptable that we allow a couple of holdout countries to prevent the adoption of European rules that deal with values central to the European project. We need to be looking immediately at another proposal for horizontal rules to combat discrimination.</del:text>
    <del:text>Thanks to this roadmap, we now have a path forward, and I am honoured to shadow its implementing strategy, but what should we do? First, we need to combat violence, including integrating consent-based rape laws. Second, we must ensure equality in all areas of life and work, and this means gender mainstreaming and gender budgeting. It is not an ideology.
Commissioner Lahbib is not here with us, but I want Commissioner MГғВ®nzatu to tell her that we really rely on her, because promoting equality is the key to a future where women ГўВҖВ“ but eventually all of us ГўВҖВ“ can live free from fear and discrimination. And the EU needs to lead this gender equality fight that we have worldwide, especially in those insecure times when geo-policy is changing.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T21:25:14</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:09:20</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_123"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_121"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_168"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_169"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_292">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_292</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Ioan-RareГ…Вҹ Bogdan</del:name>
    <del:platform>EU Parliament</del:platform>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PPE"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_345">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_345</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Frieden gilt Ihnen als VerratГӮВ ГўВҖВ“ das erinnert an George Orwell. Sie sagen Verteidigung und meinen Angriff. Sie sind dabei, einen Krieg gegen Russland vorzubereiten. Einige trГғВӨumen sogar von franzГғВ¶sischen Atomwaffen fГғВјr die EU, auch wenn die Reichweite der franzГғВ¶sischen Bomber nur bis Hannover langt. Die Zeit der Illusionen ist vorbei, sagte Frau von der Leyen heute. Dies sollte allerdings vor allem fГғВјr die hemmungslose SelbstГғВјberschГғВӨtzung der EU gelten, bei der man sich an das deutsche Kaiserreich erinnert fГғВјhlt. Die EU verkommt zum Europa der RГғВјstungskonzerne, fГғВјr deren Profite Sie ГғВјber Leichen gehen. Die Kriegskredite mГғВјssen gestoppt werden, wir brauchen Entspannungspolitik.
(Die Rednerin lehnt eine Frage nach dem Verfahren der ГўВҖВһblauen KarteГўВҖВң von Virginijus SinkeviГ„ВҚius ab.)</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T18:36:35</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_249"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_344"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_345"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_44">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_44</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Je ne sais pas si la commissaire est en train dГўВҖВҷavoir des rГғВ©unions avec des lobbys ou avec des banques pour continuer ГғВ  dГғВ©rГғВ©guler le devoir de vigilance, mais je pense quГўВҖВҷon ne peut pas avoir de dГғВ©bat aussi important que celui-ci sans la prГғВ©sence de la Commission europГғВ©enne.
Aussi, je vous demanderai sГўВҖВҷil est possible dГўВҖВҷenvisager de reprogrammer ce dГғВ©bat, pour sГўВҖВҷassurer que la Commission europГғВ©enne sera prГғВ©sente et que, au bout dГўВҖВҷun moment, elle arrГғВӘte de nous manquer de respect, comme elle lГўВҖВҷa fait ГғВ  de trop nombreuses reprises, malheureusement.</del:text>
    <del:text>But none of this would have been necessary if we had a Commission that was more preoccupied with creating growth instead of bureaucracy. If you had a Commission that was willing to prioritise within the EUR 1.2 trillion budget. Ursula von der Leyen, you are making the Europeans into welfare junkies and you're doing it from borrowed money.
So let me put this very simple. We want our money back!
NГғВҘr vi ser pГғВҘ det fra et dansk perspektiv, mГғВҘ man sige, at EU har gjort meget lidt. Igen og igen har Danmark stГғВёttet Ukraine militГғВҰrt og ГғВёkonomisk, og igen og igen har vi set, hvordan de stГғВёrste EU medlemsstater; Tyskland, Frankrig, Italien og Spanien ikke har fulgt trop. SГғВҘ det er let at give Trump skylden for den situation, Ukraine stГғВҘr i. Men hvis man virkelig vil forstГғВҘ, hvorfor vi tre ГғВҘr inde i krigen har et EU, der ikke er i stand til at forsvare sig selv, har et EU, der ikke er i stand til at forsvare Ukraine, sГғВҘ skal vi se indad. Der har vГғВҰret alt for lidt handling og alt for meget snak, og det fortsГғВҰtter desvГғВҰrre.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T18:00:04</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T10:40:06</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_23"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_37"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_43"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_44"/>
  </rdf:Description>
