  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_369">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_369</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Ukraina ingick BudapestuppgГғВ¶relsen 1994, varpГғВҘ man gav upp sina kГғВӨrnvapen. I gengГғВӨld fГғВ¶rsГғВӨkrade Ryssland att inte anvГғВӨnda vГғВҘld eller hota Ukrainas territoriella integritet och politiska sjГғВӨlvstГғВӨndighet. Ryssland bryter det lГғВ¶ftet varje dag. Vi fГғВҘr inte vara naiva. Om vi inte vill riskera att Putins erГғВ¶vringskrig fortsГғВӨtter lГғВӨngre in i Europa ГўВҖВ“ i ett lГғВӨge dГғВӨr Trumps uttalanden vГғВӨcker frГғВҘgor kring USA:s lojalitet och intressen ГўВҖВ“ behГғВ¶ver vi skaffa oss en egen trovГғВӨrdig avskrГғВӨckningsfГғВ¶rmГғВҘga, vilket i klartext betyder en stГғВ¶rre kГғВӨrnvapenarsenal.
I en perfekt vГғВӨrld hade vi inte haft nГғВҘgra kГғВӨrnvapen. Men sГғВҘ lГғВӨnge som den europeiska avskrГғВӨckningsfГғВ¶rmГғВҘgan i praktiken bygger pГғВҘ amerikansk fГғВ¶rmГғВҘga ГғВӨger inte vi vГғВҘr egen sГғВӨkerhet.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T19:06:23</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_218"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_368"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_369"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_144">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_144</del:identifier>
    <del:text></del:text>
    <del:text>Eppure, piГғВ№ di una donna su quattro nell'Unione europea vive con una disabilitГғВ . Queste donne devono affrontare doppie e triple discriminazioni: come donne, come persone con disabilitГғВ  e, in molti casi, anche in base alla loro etГғВ  o condizioni socio economiche. Diciamo basta a queste donne invisibili. Diamo loro voce.
Ci aspettiamo, allora, che questa tabella di marcia riconosca esplicitamente anche i diritti delle persone delle donne con disabilitГғВ , promuovendo misure concrete per garantire loro accesso al lavoro, all'indipendenza economica, protezione dalla violenza e dagli abusi, diritto alla salute e alla maternitГғВ , paritГғВ  nell'educazione, nella formazione, nella partecipazione politica.
La credibilitГғВ  di questa tabella si giocherГғВ  sull'inclusione di queste donne: diamo aiuto a queste donne, e ci aiuti, Commissaria.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T20:48:19</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T13:38:20</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_111"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_105"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_143"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_144"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_149">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_149</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Yet their greatest threat is Russia. The terrorist state does not only focus on Ukraine. No. They are trying their best to destabilise Moldova, an EU candidate country. This is why our job is to ensure that not a single cent of this facility benefits those who seek to undermine Moldova's sovereignty.
While the facility is a positive step, the ultimate goal is to ensure long-term stability and prosperity in the region. Moldova's future lies in Europe, where democracy and security prevail.</del:text>
    <del:text>VykonГ…ВЎtruovanГғВ© sГғВәdne procesy proti niekoГ„ВҫkГғВҪm stovkГғВЎm odporcov komunistickГғВ©ho reГ…Вҫimu naprieГ„ВҚ EurГғВіpou sprevГғВЎdzala masГғВӯvna mediГғВЎlna kampaГ…ВҲ. PouГ„ВҚenГғВЎ z naГ…ВЎej vlastnej histГғВіrie mi dovoГ„Вҫte byГ…ВҘ troГ…ВЎiГ„ВҚku kritickejГ…ВЎou k tomu, Г„ВҚo novinГғВЎri dokГғВЎГ…Вҫu vyprodukovaГ…ВҘ. VykonГ…ВЎtruovanГғВ© sГғВәdne procesy komunistickej strany v Г„ВҢeskoslovensku zapoГ„ВҚali aj priГ„ВҚinenГғВӯm doktora Rudolfa SlГғВЎnskГғВ©ho. PrГғВӯkladom nГғВЎm vГ…ВЎak nech je Г…Вҫivot Milady HorГғВЎkovej a jej podobnГғВҪm vzГғВЎcnym duГ…ВЎiam.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T20:55:08</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T13:44:57</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_64"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_109"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_148"/>
