  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_391">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_391</del:identifier>
    <del:text>MГғВЎr nem elГғВ©g, hogy belГғВјlrГ…В‘l bomlasztja, Putyin utasГғВӯtГғВЎsai alapjГғВЎn elutasГғВӯt mindent, ami Ukrajna tГғВЎmogatГғВЎsГғВЎrГғВіl szГғВіl, de a mГғВәlt hГғВ©ten egy olyan tГғВ¶rvГғВ©nyjavaslatot kezdemГғВ©nyeztek, amely lehetГ…В‘vГғВ© fogja tenni, hogy magyar ГғВЎllampolgГғВЎrokat, a kormГғВЎnynak nem tetszГ…В‘ civileket ГғВ©s politikusokat szГғВЎmГ…Вұzzenek az orszГғВЎgbГғВіl. Ez orszГғВЎgom EurГғВіpa TanГғВЎcsbГғВіl tГғВ¶rtГғВ©nГ…В‘ kilГғВ©pГғВ©sГғВ©t jelentenГғВ© azonnal, amely egy hatalmas lГғВ©pГғВ©s az EurГғВіpai UniГғВі elhagyГғВЎsa felГғВ©. De nem fogjuk hagyni, EurГғВіpa erГ…В‘sebb, ГғВ©s ГғВӯgy MagyarorszГғВЎg is erГ…В‘sebb lesz OrbГғВЎn nГғВ©lkГғВјl.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T19:34:28</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_279"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_390"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_391"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_191">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_191</del:identifier>
    <del:text>O objetivo ГғВ© que possamos garantir que as geraГғВ§ГғВөes futuras tenham acesso a ГғВЎgua para consumo e tambГғВ©m para as vГғВЎrias atividades econГғВіmicas, particularmente a agricultura.
O sul da Europa e, particularmente, Portugal sofrem atualmente uma elevada escassez de ГғВЎgua. No nosso caso, as regiГғВөes do Alentejo e do Algarve sГғВЈo as mais afetadas.
Portugal apresentou ontem a EstratГғВ©gia Nacional para a GestГғВЈo da ГғВҒgua, que tem por nome ГӮВ«ГғВҒgua que uneГӮВ», que prevГғВӘ resolver a escassez de ГғВЎgua, quer para consumo humano quer para outras utilizaГғВ§ГғВөes. EstГғВЎ previsto um investimento de mais de 5ГӮВ milГӮВ milhГғВөes de euros.ГӮВ Por isso, espero que a UniГғВЈo Europeia seja solidГғВЎria, que assuma as suas responsabilidades e que ajude os Estados-Membros.
ГғВҒgua ГғВ© vida nos territГғВіrios, ГғВЎgua ГғВ© coesГғВЈo social, ГғВЎgua ГғВ© economia, ГғВЎgua ГғВ© seguranГғВ§a. Sim, falo da ГғВЎgua e da ГғВЎgua que nos une na UniГғВЈo Europeia.</del:text>
    <del:text>We are looking forward to these new initiatives while Member States implement the legislation that has recently been adopted. I can also inform you that the Polish Presidency will be hosting the informal meeting of equality ministers in April. Let us move forward together and make equality a reality for all women and men, boys and girls.</del:text>
