  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_332">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_332</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Pat tad, kad pirms trim gadiem Krievija iebruka UkrainГ„ВҒ, mГ…В«su lГ„В«deri joprojГ„ВҒm nesaprata vai negribГ„В“ja saprast, kГ„ВҒdГ„ВҒ situГ„ВҒcijГ„ВҒ mГ„В“s esam. Tikai tagad, kad amerikГ„ВҒГ…ВҶi ir parГ„ВҒdГ„В«juГ…ВЎi mГ…В«su vГ„ВҒjumu, mГ„В“s kaut ko cenГ…ВЎamies darГ„В«t.
Tagad tiek paziГ…ВҶots par 800 miljardiem lielu ieguldГ„В«jumu Eiropas droГ…ВЎГ„В«bГ„ВҒ, bet tГ„ВҒ ir tikai un vienГ„В«gi iespГ„В“ja aizГ…ВҶemties. Vai mГ„В“s gribam vГ„В“l vienu inflГ„ВҒcijas vilni? Vai mГ„В“s gribam vГ„В“l vairГ„ВҒk samazinГ„ВҒt Eiropas konkurГ„В“tspГ„В“ju? NekavГ„В“joГ…ВЎi ir pilnГ„В«bГ„ВҒ jГ„ВҒatceГ„Вј zaГ„Вјais kurss un visa nauda jГ„ВҒnovirza aizsardzГ„В«bas industrijai. Ja mГ„В“s to neizdarГ„В«sim tГ…В«lГ„В«t, tad mГ„В“s neizglГ„ВҒbsim ne klimatu, ne droГ…ВЎГ„В«bu.</del:text>
