  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_478">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_478</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Necesitamos fondos para apoyar a trabajadores y empresas en su transiciГғВіn hacia una industria limpia y digitalizada. Y para que este proceso pueda llevarse a cabo con ГғВ©xito debe hacerse a travГғВ©s del diГғВЎlogo social con los agentes sociales. Por ello, serГғВӯa necesario contar con una Directiva para la transiciГғВіn justa que permita adelantarse a estas situaciones de transiciГғВіn.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T21:24:44</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_343"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_477"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_478"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_167">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_167</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Na UniГғВЈo Europeia, enfrentamos desafios semelhantes. Temos o direito de saber para onde vai o dinheiro dos nossos contribuintes, que projetos sГғВЈo financiados, quem beneficia dos fundos europeus destinados ГғВ  Ajuda PГғВәblica ao Desenvolvimento.
Que think tanks, que ГғВіrgГғВЈos de comunicaГғВ§ГғВЈo social foram financiados pela ComissГғВЈo Europeia? Que polГғВӯtica estamos, sem saber, a subsidiar?ГӮВ Sem respostas claras, a confianГғВ§a nas instituiГғВ§ГғВөes europeias ГғВ© abalada e a democracia, enfraquecida.
ГғВү imperativo criar um Departamento Europeu para a EficiГғВӘncia Governamental. Este organismo vai garantir que cada euro ГғВ© gasto de forma transparente e responsГғВЎvel, assegurando que os financiamentos nГғВЈo servem interesses ocultos, mas, sim, o bem comum.</del:text>
    <del:text></del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T21:22:12</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:07:07</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_122"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_118"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_166"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_167"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_33">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_33</del:identifier>
    <del:name>JoГғВЈo Oliveira</del:name>
    <del:name>Milan UhrГғВӯk</del:name>
    <del:platform>EU Parliament</del:platform>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_The_Left"/>
