  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_227">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_227</del:identifier>
    <del:text>ГҺВҷГҺВҙГҺВ№ГҺВұГҺВҜГҸВ„ГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВұ ГҺВіГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҺВјГҺВ№ГҺВәГҸВҒГҸВҢГҸВ„ГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВұ ГҺВәГҸВҒГҺВ¬ГҸВ„ГҺВ· ГҺВјГҺВӯГҺВ»ГҺВ·, ГҸВҢГҸВҖГҸВүГҸВӮ ГҺВ· ГҸВҖГҺВұГҸВ„ГҸВҒГҺВҜГҺВҙГҺВұ ГҺВјГҺВҝГҸВ… ГҺВ· ГҺВҡГҸВҚГҸВҖГҸВҒГҺВҝГҸВӮ, ГҺВ· ГҺВәГҺВҝГҺВ№ГҺВҪГҺВ® ГҸВҖГҸВҒГҺВҝГҺВјГҺВ®ГҺВёГҺВөГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВҶГҺВұГҸВҒГҺВјГҺВ¬ГҺВәГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҺВјГҸВҖГҺВҝГҸВҒГҺВөГҺВҜ ГҺВҪГҺВұ ГҺВәГҺВ¬ГҺВҪГҺВөГҺВ№ ГҸВ„ГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВ¬ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҺВҙГҺВ№ГҺВұГҸВҶГҺВҝГҸВҒГҺВ¬ ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВ· ГҺВҙГҺВ№ГҺВұГҺВёГҺВөГҸВғГҺВ№ГҺВјГҸВҢГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҺВәГҺВұГҺВ№ ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВҝ ГҺВәГҸВҢГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВӮ ГҸВ„ГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҸВҶГҺВұГҸВҒГҺВјГҺВ¬ГҺВәГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҺВіГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҺВҪ ГҺВұГҸВғГҺВёГҺВөГҺВҪГҺВ®. ГҺВӨГҺВұГҸВ…ГҸВ„ГҸВҢГҸВҮГҸВҒГҺВҝГҺВҪГҺВұ, ГҸВҖГҸВҒГҺВӯГҸВҖГҺВөГҺВ№ ГҺВҪГҺВұ ГҺВҙГҺВ№ГҺВұГҸВғГҸВҶГҺВұГҺВ»ГҺВҜГҸВғГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВјГҺВө ГҸВҢГҸВ„ГҺВ№ ГҺВ· ГҺВұГҸВғГҸВҶГҺВ¬ГҺВ»ГҺВөГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҸВҶГҺВұГҸВҒГҺВјГҺВ¬ГҺВәГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҺВұГҺВәГҺВҝГҺВ»ГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВёГҺВөГҺВҜ ГҸВ„ГҺВұ ГҺВұГҸВ…ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҸВҒГҺВ¬ ГҺВәГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҸВ„ГҺВ®ГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВҖГҺВҝГҸВ… ГҺВёГҺВӯГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВјГҺВө ГҺВіГҺВ№ГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҺВҪ ГҸВ…ГҺВіГҺВөГҺВҜГҺВұ ГҺВәГҺВұГҺВ№ ГҺВөГҸВ…ГҺВ·ГҺВјГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВҜГҺВұ ГҸВ„ГҸВүГҺВҪ ГҸВҖГҺВҝГҺВ»ГҺВ№ГҸВ„ГҸВҺГҺВҪ ГҺВјГҺВұГҸВӮ. ГҺВҹГҺВ№ ГҸВҖГҸВҒГҸВүГҸВ„ГҺВҝГҺВІГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВ»ГҺВҜГҺВөГҸВӮ ГҸВ„ГҺВ·ГҸВӮ ГҺВ•ГҸВ…ГҸВҒГҸВүГҸВҖГҺВұГҸВҠГҺВәГҺВ®ГҸВӮ ГҺВҲГҺВҪГҸВүГҸВғГҺВ·ГҸВӮ ГҺВӯГҸВҮГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВҪ ГҺВ®ГҺВҙГҺВ· ГҺВұГҸВҖГҺВҝГҺВҙГҺВөГҺВҜГҺВҫГҺВөГҺВ№ ГҸВҢГҸВ„ГҺВ№ ГҺВҝГҺВ№ ГҺВәГҺВҝГҺВ№ГҺВҪГҺВӯГҸВӮ ГҺВҙГҸВҒГҺВ¬ГҸВғГҺВөГҺВ№ГҸВӮ ГҺВөГҸВҖГҺВ№ГҸВ„ГҸВҒГҺВӯГҸВҖГҺВҝГҸВ…ГҺВҪ ГҸВ„ГҺВұГҸВҮГҸВҚГҸВ„ГҺВөГҸВҒГҺВөГҸВӮ ГҺВәГҺВұГҺВ№ ГҸВҖГҺВ№ГҺВҝ ГҺВұГҸВҖГҺВҝГҸВ„ГҺВөГҺВ»ГҺВөГҸВғГҺВјГҺВұГҸВ„ГҺВ№ГҺВәГҺВӯГҸВӮ ГҺВұГҺВҪГҸВ„ГҺВ№ГҺВҙГҸВҒГҺВ¬ГҸВғГҺВөГҺВ№ГҸВӮ ГҸВғГҺВө ГҸВ…ГҺВіГҺВөГҺВ№ГҺВҝГҺВҪГҺВҝГҺВјГҺВ№ГҺВәГҺВӯГҸВӮ ГҺВәГҸВҒГҺВҜГҸВғГҺВөГҺВ№ГҸВӮ ГҺВәГҺВұГҺВ№ ГҸВҖГҸВҒГҺВҝГҺВәГҺВ»ГҺВ®ГҸВғГҺВөГҺВ№ГҸВӮ. ГҺВЈГҺВұГҸВӮ ГҺВөГҸВ…ГҸВҮГҺВұГҸВҒГҺВ№ГҸВғГҸВ„ГҸВҺ.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:30:31</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_169"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_226"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_227"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_113">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_113</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Rihards Kols</del:name>
    <del:name>Beatrice Timgren</del:name>
    <del:platform>EU Parliament</del:platform>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_ECR"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_178">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_178</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Mientras tanto, en este Parlamento tenemos varios grupos parlamentarios que aplauden las medidas de Trump y algunos de ellos hasta se arrodillan ante sus intereses y luego se hacen llamar ГӮВ«PatriotasГӮВ». ГӮВҝPatriotas de quГғВ©? De la ГғВәnica patria que entienden: la del dinero y la del poder.
Por eso, yo animo al conjunto de los grupos parlamentarios democrГғВЎticos a que protejamos Europa, a que protejamos a la mayorГғВӯa trabajadora, a que protejamos nuestros puestos de trabajo; a que lo hagamos con mГғВЎs reindustrializaciГғВіn, con mГғВЎs polГғВӯticas de cohesiГғВіn, con mГғВЎs polГғВӯticas de integraciГғВіn; y a que lo hagamos para protegernos de las polГғВӯticas de Trump, pero tambiГғВ©n de las polГғВӯticas de aquellos que desde aquГғВӯ trabajan para los intereses de las grandes multinacionales.</del:text>
    <del:text>There is a desperate need for progress and real equality, as the people marching on the streets all over Europe on 8ГӮВ March showed it very clearly, so we have to listen to those voices. As our feminist and democratic values are under attack, there is no middle ground or room for hesitation. It's either mainstreaming gender equality or mainstreaming misogyny and sexism. You have our fullest support, Commissioner, on this roadmap, and the S&amp;D Group is with you.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T21:37:08</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:23:08</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_129"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_130"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_177"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_178"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_118">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_118</del:identifier>
    <del:text></del:text>
    <del:text>We vote on the appointment of Slavka Eley.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T19:58:59</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T12:56:44</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_85"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_117"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_118"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_125">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_125</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Cele 1,9 miliarde de euro nu sunt doar un cec de solidaritate, ci un angajament ferm pentru modernizare, stabilitate ГҲВҷi integrare europeanГ„Вғ.ГӮВ Aceste fonduri trebuie sГ„Вғ producГ„Вғ rezultate vizibile pentru cetГ„ВғГҲВӣeni.
Am propus amendamente esenГҲВӣiale care au fost adoptate ГҲВҷi care vor contribui direct la succesul acestui plan ГҲВҷi le mulГҲВӣumesc raportorilor:
- sprijinirea zonelor rurale ГҲВҷi a politicilor pentru copii, fonduri europene care au sГ„Вғ ajungГ„Вғ acolo unde este cea mai mare nevoie,
- implicarea diasporei ГғВ®n implementarea mГ„Вғsurilor ГўВҖВ“ milioane de moldoveni trГ„Вғiesc ГҲВҷi muncesc ГғВ®n alte state europene ГҲВҷi vor juca astfel un rol esenГҲВӣial ГғВ®n dezvoltarea ГҲВӣГ„Вғrii,
- investiГҲВӣii strategice ГғВ®n interconectГ„Вғri cu RomГғВўnia, mai ales pe zona de energie.
Mai mult, pentru utilizarea eficientГ„Вғ a acestor fonduri am propus ГҲВҷi se va deschide chiar acum, s-a aprobat, un birou al Parlamentului European la ChiГҲВҷinГ„Вғu, o iniГҲВӣiativГ„Вғ pe care am avut-o ГғВ®n calitate de vicepreГҲВҷedinte al Parlamentului European, responsabil de relaГҲВӣia cu Republica Moldova.
IatГ„Вғ cГ„Вғ Republica Moldova are uГҲВҷa deschisГ„Вғ ГғВ®n Europa. Europa sprijinГ„Вғ Republica Moldova. Republica Moldova are o oportunitate istoricГ„Вғ pe care nu o poate rata.
AveГҲВӣi tot sprijinul din partea Parlamentului European.</del:text>
    <del:text>The first speaker, speaking on behalf of the Council, will be Mr SzГ…ВӮapka, Poland's Minister for European Union Affairs.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T20:19:03</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T13:08:42</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_92"/>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_124"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_125"/>
  </rdf:Description>
