  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_273">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_273</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Time and time again, we have warned about the dangers of illegal migration, and time and time again we have been dismissed, ignored and vilified. How many more Europeans must die, be raped, robbed, attacked before you wake up? How many more grieving families must be left behind in sorrow and despair before we take this serious? For every victim, every shattered family, we must say: naГғВҜve policies cost lives.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T16:46:43</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_37"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_272"/>
    <del:follows rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_273"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_158">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_158</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Ignazio Roberto Marino</del:name>
    <del:platform>EU Parliament</del:platform>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_Verts_ALE"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_179">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_179</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Pourtant, ici, pas dГўВҖВҷexpression, pas de rГғВ©solution pour exiger sa libГғВ©ration immГғВ©diate, celle du plus ancien prisonnier politique dГўВҖВҷEurope. Pas un mot pour GeorgesГӮВ IbrahimГӮВ Abdallah, pourtant libГғВ©rable depuis vingt-cinq ans. Ici, cГўВҖВҷest toujours cette mГғВӘme hypocrisie des bourgeois bien-pensants et de leur ГӮВ«deux poids, deux mesuresГӮВ».
La cour dГўВҖВҷappel de Paris, qui devait se prononcer le 20ГӮВ fГғВ©vrier dernier sur sa libГғВ©ration, a ajournГғВ© sa dГғВ©cision au 19ГӮВ juin prochain. Le maintien en dГғВ©tention de GeorgesГӮВ IbrahimГӮВ Abdallah est un scandale dГўВҖВҷГғВүtat et une honte pour lГўВҖВҷГғВүtat franГғВ§ais. Assez dГўВҖВҷacharnement! LibГғВ©rez GeorgesГӮВ IbrahimГӮВ Abdallah! LibГғВ©rez GeorgesГӮВ IbrahimГӮВ Abdallah!</del:text>
    <del:text>IstraГ…Вҫivanje objavljeno u studenom proГ…ВЎle godine pokazuje kako je nasilje nad Г…Вҫenama i dalje gotovo obiГ„ВҚajno, Г„ВҚak i u Europi. Svaka treГ„ВҮa Г…Вҫena doГ…Вҫivjela je fiziГ„ВҚko ili seksualno nasilje u odrasloj dobi, a svaka peta se suoГ„ВҚila s obiteljskim nasiljem.
I dok stariji oblici nasilja nad Г…Вҫenama nisu iskorijenjeni, naГ…Вҫalost svjedoГ„ВҚimo novima. Posljednje godiГ…ВЎnje izvjeГ…ВЎГ„ВҮe o ravnopravnosti spolova ukazuje kako je nasilje nad Г…Вҫenama na internetu postalo sveprisutno. Od 2023. godine 97 posto online prijava seksualnog zlostavljanja djece na internetu odnosilo se na seksualno zlostavljanje djevojaka i djevojГ„ВҚica.
Europska unija ima najnaprednije zakonodavstvo koje obuhvaГ„ВҮa zaГ…ВЎtitu od nasilja na internetu, ukljuГ„ВҚujuГ„ВҮi nasilje koje se temelji na neetiГ„ВҚkom koriГ…ВЎtenju umjetne inteligencije, ali samo zakonodavstvo nije dovoljno. Moramo educirati Г…Вҫene, a osobito djevojГ„ВҚice kako bismo se osnaГ…Вҫili u pogledu nasilja svih vrsta, ukljuГ„ВҚujuГ„ВҮi nasilje na internetu i nasilje putem druГ…ВЎtvenih mreГ…Вҫa.
Kao zastupnici u parlamentu moramo uГ„ВҚiniti sve Г…ВЎto je u naГ…ВЎoj moГ„ВҮi kako bi se Г…Вҫene osjeГ„ВҮale sigurno i slobodno.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-10T21:38:19</del:timestamp>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:24:47</del:timestamp>
